verbose_text: GEN, in the absence of catalase, reduced dose-dependently (0-100 muM) the cell viability of HT29 cells after 72 h of incubation [XREF_BIBR], whereas in our experiments no cytotoxicity was measured up to 200 muM (24 h) neither in presence nor in absence of catalase (data not shown).
evidence: catalase, reduced dose-dependently (0-100 muM) the cell viability
